{"tid":468233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港隊對黎巴嫰】足總或拍攝球迷助警執法","createTime":"2017-11-14T07:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T15:03:14.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e8367343620475f6b4ffe0e8c9aa6132cd5e9621","tid":468233,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/155201_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F155201_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a5bec4a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港足球代表隊今晚在香港大球場主場對黎巴嫩，繼續在亞洲盃外圍賽搶分。足總副主席貝鈞奇預料，今晚繼續會有少量球迷會噓國歌，但他提醒球迷，亞洲足協今晚將會派人監場，呼籲球迷停止噓國歌、尊重自己及國歌，同時避免香港足總與港隊被處分。貝表示，足總或研究在《國歌法》本地立法後，拍攝球迷，協助警方執法。<br />\n<br />\n今晚八時，港隊將於香港大球場迎戰黎巴嫩。香港隊今晚需要搶得分數，才能保持出線希望。上月底，亞洲足協就港隊上月初主場對大馬的球迷噓國歌作出警告，惟上週對巴林的友誼賽，繼續有球迷噓國歌及展示不文手勢。<br />\n<br />\n香港足球總會副主席貝鈞奇預料，今晚將會繼續有少量球迷噓國歌，但他提醒球迷，亞洲足協今晚肯定會派員監察球場。他呼籲球迷要尊重自己、尊重國歌，停止噓國歌的行為，以免香港足總被亞洲足協再處分。貝強調，如亞洲足協加強懲處，處分包括罰款、閉門作賽。足總及場地保安今晚會加強人手管理，警方亦會派員進入球場。<br />\n<br />\n中共人大常委會已將《國歌法》納入香港《基本法》附件三，特區政府將展開本地立法。貝鈞奇又表示，《國歌法》一旦本地立法，球迷將不會「以身試法」噓國歌。香港足總將會檢討在法例生效後，需否協助警方執法，措施或包括拍攝市民噓國歌，再交給執法部門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/貝鈞奇料球迷續噓國歌-足總或拍攝球迷噓國歌助警執法/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%B2%9D%E9%88%9E%E5%A5%87%E6%96%99%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E7%BA%8C%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E8%B6%B3%E7%B8%BD%E6%88%96%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E5%8A%A9%E8%AD%A6%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%2F&d=qH46E849tL3G9a%2FQy7lHyQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e11dfd5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%B2%9D%E9%88%9E%E5%A5%87%E6%96%99%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E7%BA%8C%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E8%B6%B3%E7%B8%BD%E6%88%96%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E5%8A%A9%E8%AD%A6%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%2F&h=bc3d25d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/貝鈞奇料球迷續噓國歌-足總或拍攝球迷噓國歌助警執法/</a>"},{"pid":"dd1dcd4ce770d24e00e18f318501063f01c4d0ba","tid":468233,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a721b8cdef4974e41f175f4705ccda5342d2c448","tid":468233,"uid":130247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf817868a4e1ba9b1c500ae7bb47b17b7d70a73","tid":468233,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccf2c3da713f512d5dea29e3e890e1aa930c198","tid":468233,"uid":76745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾 提昇香港足球既野又唔見你班契弟做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ce46e13ee885e54ef4b9b5d88b51dd15ede7c8","tid":468233,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃撚圾 提昇香港足球既野又唔見你班契弟做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5285b51f372815203c80b42548540c08535fa8","tid":468233,"uid":37463,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"未立法都唔俾噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做乜鳩"},{"pid":"1f68e89c6c26d739010df26b2a86f404bb37029f","tid":468233,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚痴線<br />\n所有機構都與人民為敵"},{"pid":"8d4fa7d0b9d9559f9f2834bee79351434d260086","tid":468233,"uid":31,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201